window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Before Joe Hart can stop the murder of John Lennon, he must die himself.</b></p> <p>When Joe Hart dies after leading a wasted life, he chooses to use his second chance to make the world better.</p> <p>Even when he thinks he knows what is coming, changing the past is difficult.</p> <p>What would you do, if you could do it all again?</p> <p><i>Includes a special bonus note read by the author.</i></p>"; 
